<item chapterid="596171" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1929" articlename="绝世高手" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521473896" lastupdate="1521473896" chaptername="第214章摄人心魄" chapterorder="214" size="6298" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    就在这时，一个男人淡淡的声音传了进来。

    “墨格西，站起来！”

