<item chapterid="596741" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1929" articlename="绝世高手" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521473896" lastupdate="1521473896" chaptername="第784章巡海使" chapterorder="784" size="6271" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    陈离说道：“骗你麻痹啊！”他恼火道：“你们都是猪脑子啊！老子存心要定海珠，之前就不会给。我不给，你们也没办法。我至于去偷吗？”

